.section-grouping
  %h2(id="release-highlights") Release Highlights

  %ul
    %li(id="highlight-asl")
      Aeolus now licensed under Apache Software License (ASL).

    %li(id="highlight-eventapi")
      Added Conductor support for the Event API. This API provides Conductor with a means for tracking system messages, such as instance changes.

    %li(id="highlight-i18n")
      Improved i18n in API error codes and messages.

    %li(id="highlight-status")
      Aeolus now checks the status on image builds and pushes from ImageFactory. This helps Conductor track image building, pushing or readiness for deployment use.

    %li(id="highlight-securityfix")
      Security fix removes logging of sensitive SQL occurring with RPM installation of Conductor.

    %li(id="highlight-deleteproviderimage")
      Aeolus now indicates the remaining provider content after deleting a single provider image.

    %li(id="highlight-imageimport")
      Conductor now supports image imports with the web interface. This provides users with the ability to import an image from a provider via Conductor.

%br

